D . R . Horton increases credit facility . D . R . Horton Inc said Monday that its unsecured bank credit facility has been increased to $ 625 million from $ 400 million . The member bank facility was led by NationsBank , Bank of America and Fleet National Bank . In a press release , , Horton said the credit facility consists of a $ 200 million five - year term loan , a $ 400 million four - year revolving loan facility and a $ 25 million four - year letter of credit facility . 
